ising platform powered by real-time mobile audiences.\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We deliver hundreds of millions of ads per day across more than 500,000 active apps.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our platform uses artificial intelligence to deliver more efficient, effective, and precise digital advertising campaigns.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our direct integration with thousands of mobile publishers gives us access to more than 50 billion first-party data signals per day across the globe.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marketers use these anonymized signals to understand and predict consumer behavior, identify new opportunities, and fuel business growth.\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Contact Information  Maya CarmelyDirector of Marketingmaya.carmely@start.io  SOURCE:Start.io    View the original press release on newswire.com.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3557, \"end\": 3561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maya_peoples\", \"score\": 0.9927224133555118, \"rank\": 0.006523391577678856, \"text\": \"Maya\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maya_peoples\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maya_peoples\"}]}]}"